  "detailed_description": "Learn the story of Priscilla, the Perfect Soldier (PS) of the United Earth Federation, awakened from the cryptosleep to stop an alien invasion.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1328510/extras/1559c3b9a178b8bdd53989367361df87.avif?t=1679397797\" width=614 height=148 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Stop the invasion </h2><br>Fight many of dangerous alliens across 10 levels to reach the orbit of the Moon and destroy the alien leader.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1328510/extras/28b901fb3b06355d1d6949b25a57548e.poster.avif?t=1679397797\" width=614 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1328510/extras/28b901fb3b06355d1d6949b25a57548e.webm?t=1679397797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1328510/extras/28b901fb3b06355d1d6949b25a57548e.mp4?t=1679397797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Use bonuses </h2><br>Catch the supplies dropped by Federation's Support to power up your ship.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1328510/extras/8799fc2fd5da89b9d8d81791c5f1bb1b.avif?t=1679397797\" width=614 height=130 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Repair kit</strong> - restores 5 units of HP to your ship<br></li><li> <strong>Energy shield</strong> - protects the ship from receiving 10 damage units<br></li><li> <strong>Weapon booster</strong> - for 10 seconds activates an additional weapon module of the ship with more powerful guns<br></li><li> <strong>Stasis generator</strong> - slows down time by 10 seconds, helping to dodge opponents and their bullets</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Become the Perfect Soldier </h2><br>The passage of each level is rated:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>1 star</strong> - for passing<br></li><li> <strong>2 stars</strong> - for getting >70% of the maximum PTS<br></li><li> <strong>3 stars</strong> - for getting >90% of the maximum PTS</li></ul><br>Will you be able to complete all the levels and get 3 stars?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1328510/extras/232c8d7ec72eaa3671ce4993733ea77a.avif?t=1679397797\" width=614 height=130 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Learn the story of Priscilla, the Perfect Soldier (PS) of the United Earth Federation, awakened from the cryptosleep to stop an alien invasion.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1328510/extras/1559c3b9a178b8bdd53989367361df87.avif?t=1679397797\" width=614 height=148 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Stop the invasion </h2><br>Fight many of dangerous alliens across 10 levels to reach the orbit of the Moon and destroy the alien leader.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1328510/extras/28b901fb3b06355d1d6949b25a57548e.poster.avif?t=1679397797\" width=614 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1328510/extras/28b901fb3b06355d1d6949b25a57548e.webm?t=1679397797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1328510/extras/28b901fb3b06355d1d6949b25a57548e.mp4?t=1679397797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Use bonuses </h2><br>Catch the supplies dropped by Federation's Support to power up your ship.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1328510/extras/8799fc2fd5da89b9d8d81791c5f1bb1b.avif?t=1679397797\" width=614 height=130 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Repair kit</strong> - restores 5 units of HP to your ship<br></li><li> <strong>Energy shield</strong> - protects the ship from receiving 10 damage units<br></li><li> <strong>Weapon booster</strong> - for 10 seconds activates an additional weapon module of the ship with more powerful guns<br></li><li> <strong>Stasis generator</strong> - slows down time by 10 seconds, helping to dodge opponents and their bullets</li></ul><h2 class=\"b